{"tid":334323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日睇咗未？陪伴32年 微軟宣布踢走「小畫家」","createTime":"2017-07-24T14:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T17:08:17.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0111341872218bb4f921f91de4ae7ca4e4632904","tid":334323,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170724/_2017072419595685807.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170724%2F_2017072419595685807.jpg&h=10bee51d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信對於每一位Windows用家來說，「小畫家」(Microsoft Paint)並不陌生，雖然功能比不上Photoshop、<a href=\"http://Paint.Net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FPaint.Net&d=axfG9w7FiuduG36e9geNTqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=8f175e59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Paint.Net</a>等，但仍是不少人學用電腦時的第一套繪圖程式。不過微軟今日宣佈，將在新版Windows 10 Fall Creators Update踢走「小畫家」。<br />\n<br />\n「小畫家」是微軟由1985年Windows1.0時就推出的繪畫程式，伴隨著Windows系列32年。微軟於今年4月宣布，將「小畫家」改版成 「小畫家3D」。至今日，微軟又宣布，將「小畫家」列入放棄開發的程式清單，相信在將來推出幾個更新系統後，終有一天會被正式移除。<br />\n<br />\n另外，除了棄用「小畫家」外，另一款大家熟悉的「Outlook Express」亦將被移除。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/963684/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F963684%2F&d=axfG9w7FiuduG36e9geNTqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=2cc1a9bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F963684%2F&h=77301401\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/963684/</a>"},{"pid":"c1acfb9d6422d3d942c8c06f1fefa0fb0fb0cb2e","tid":334323,"uid":91492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 靜係識用小畫家"},{"pid":"50633ef14bbcb4ed4dcfd18c805ee2eb25fe693c","tid":334323,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislik